channel.title: Runescape communitys, and which are better?
channel.description:
Hey, I'm wondering which rs community to use.. I've hurd of a few new ones, at the moment I've been using easygp I hurd powerbot scams and sythes full of scammers.
easygp is newer and doesn't have a reputation of anything, so should I just try and help easygp to get bigger?
I know powerbot pretty much blows both away because they have a bot and yeah, but we all know powerbots full of scammers.
If you don't know either community you can check out the layouts..
Sythe-www.sythe.org EasyGP-www.easygp.org
